Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…和我還喜歡他時的迪奧斯很像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你無法成為我的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…姬宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該已經說過了這並不是遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為革命的決鬥…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不要摘下來!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是以我們決鬥者代表的身份\N去面對決鬥廣場的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在整個事件了結之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們仍必須維持決鬥者的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家倒是早就已經摘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情還是早點忘了的好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能夠忘得掉嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:02:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說起來我已經忘記那個少年的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個少年?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去,在我姊姊還小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有一次差點溺死在河裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時有位少年\N為了要去救姊姊而跟著跳入河中去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然姊姊很幸運的被附近的大人救起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那位要救姊姊而跳下水的少年\N卻被河水沖走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…死了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊不久就忘了那少年的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我認為她真是個冷淡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如今我也試著去回想…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾幾何時也把他給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在會想到這些事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安希,劍給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了,在猶豫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最後你讓你的朋友陷入了不幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,一切都是我的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭這樣的我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我像過去般希望能當個王子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否就不會有人再感到痛苦了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的傷,你的痛我一直都在用身體感受著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是明知道這世界的一切\N卻仍選擇走向這條路的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道你的一切才深愛著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安希,劍給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了…乖女孩,安希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇之門…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印了讓世界革命之力的門…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安希!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…宮…不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事的勇者大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若論當朋友的滋味我是嘗到一點點了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊…姬宮…姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於人們的憎恨而閃爍的百萬支劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看到這柄王子之劍而開始興奮著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨的魔女…可恨的魔女…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為王子的替身承受這些劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是薔薇新娘的宿命…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是安希所自願的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻正是破解封印的時刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是開啟新世界之門的時刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生先生…姬宮…救救姬宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉生先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救…姬宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不要動比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下就會幫你治療的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個體貼的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有個薔薇形狀的門對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那扇門裡,有著永恆耀眼的事物與奇跡之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那力量的話就什麼都能辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是個女孩子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也沒有力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有力量的話就什麼都能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以將她從命運中解放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要如何使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由我決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,不要擺出一付哭喪的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都已經努力到現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要這麼自責了比較好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直將薔薇刻印珍惜到今日對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我給你個獎勵的吻吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我給你的安慰喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連這把劍也還是不行嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要到何時我才能取回迪奧斯的力量?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷,反正薔薇新娘是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你還能站的起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你還真的以為你能打開那扇門嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子之劍已經折斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印已經解不開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你是解不開的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑被我打敗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好,就隨你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是很像以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去也是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為一心一意是有價值的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為這是改變世界的唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是,光憑一心一意是什麼都改變不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟只能以依存於他人的形式活著罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了獲得改變世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我付出了很大的風險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮…你並不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟你在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能感到…何等的幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍都…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別打開!你曉得會發生什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮、姬宮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來…救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了見到你,我才到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以,不要怕這個我們能夠相逢的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐蒂娜…大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮…終於…能見到你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐蒂娜大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐蒂娜大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮、手給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行、您快點逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手給我…來、姬宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的!再不快逃的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬宮、快點…手給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點…快點…手給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我們會一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…我還是無法…成為王子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.82,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我…姬宮……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來卻成了場扮王子的遊戲…原諒我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐蒂娜不在家嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家本來還想和她一起寫作業的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你畢業之後要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是往高中部升上去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在說這個啦,是將來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是應該會當女演員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的認為你能當的成嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你真的認為你當的成是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就請期待十年後的同學會囉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來你自己呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是將來啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是會釣個金龜婿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來\N抓個好男人嫁不才是所謂「女人的本事」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真說得出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙最近有讓她認真的對象了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不久前還動不動就\N歐蒂娜姊姊歐蒂娜姊姊的鬼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛?你有意見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了!那個歐蒂娜姊姊是誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?你不知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想!之前不是很有名嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一直穿男裝的那個女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還常常被老師罵的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～想起來了,就是她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了!想起來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是聽說上個月還是上上個月受重傷住院去了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?住院了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼聽到的是被戀人還是朋友背叛才轉學的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我聽到的是她跟理事長發生問題才退學的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正,怎麼說都沒差了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的時機抓的不錯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下學期開始就要請你輔助我的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你增選了專攻科目?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是要將玩樂拖到的進度趕回來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩樂是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個!是!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能…能不能…能不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若～葉!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給我這最好的朋友的生日禮物準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那之後明明就沒過多久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家似乎就把她給忘得一乾二淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然她並沒有引發革命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失的她對這世界來說不過是個淘汰者罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:20:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經重新制定好薔薇的規制了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再麻煩你囉,安希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎還不知道已經引發了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請你在這舒適的棺木裡\N永遠地玩你的王子遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是,我必須要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走?去哪兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人並沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是從你的世界中消失了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等,安希!安希!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回換我找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你在哪我一定會找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等我喔…歐蒂娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了要是你有任何煩惱的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以先找我談談喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.51,0:22:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你做朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們總有一天要一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天要一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「總有一天要一起閃耀」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
